    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six power plant. This example delivers linear power through its individual throttle bodies, peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry. Equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-variable differential lock, it offers exceptional tactile feedback and corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the high-compression internals remain within factory tolerances. A driver-focused machine with excellent mechanical provenance.",
