      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive shape both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep shine with only minor road wear expected from a well-loved car. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with premium upholstery that shows very minimal aging. Mechanically, it is sound; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014function perfectly. Recent service records are available, confirming a history of proactive maintenance. It\u2019s a reliable, turn-key driver ready for its next owner.",
