    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been truly well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and absolutely ready for its next big adventure. It runs super smooth, looks sharp, and has so much life left in it! I've taken really good care of it, and I honestly think you're going to love how it handles the road. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
