      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains composed with a functional M-Variable differential lock and has received proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Suspension kinematics are tight, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and VANOS operation are exemplary. This is a visceral, analog machine optimized for the B-road enthusiast.",
